'''ACME Sales''' drives global revenue across the [[Acme Anvil|Anvil]], [[Acme Rocket|Rocket]], and [[Acme TNT|TNT]] product lines, with field teams spread across Europe and North America. The department employs 96 people and operates as the customer-facing arm of the company.

Day-to-day work is coordinated between the [[ACME Amsterdam HQ|Amsterdam headquarters]] and the [[ACME Vienna Office|Vienna office]], with the latter serving as the principal hub for the DACH and central European markets.
